welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Muscoy, a charming city known for its rich history and vibrant culture. We hope you enjoy your stay and take the time to explore all that our beautiful city has to offer."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Barstow-Daggett Airport serves all commercial flights and provides amenities for passengers.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Barstow-Daggett Airport serves private and charter flights, as well as offering services for pilots and their aircraft.

wifi.note: Passengers can access the airport's WiFi network for free by connecting to the designated network and following the instructions.
